title: #92Noon! Montage/Saunders/Bercich/Charch/Birk
description: Full show! Vikings win third straight, montage and celebrate, Wolves coach Ryan Saunders to end first hour...Pete Bercich most of the middle hour...Charch on Vikes and Fantasy, Birk on the Purple, and thoughts on the QB to wrap the show!
